绪。\n更新对应的会话状态为 RUNNING。","operationId":"handle_container_ready_api_v1_internal_containers_ready_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ContainerReadyRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/internal/containers/exited":{"post":{"tags":["internal"],"summary":"Handle Container Exited","description":"处理容器退出事件\n\n由 Executor 在关闭前调用，通知控制平面容器即将退出。","operationId":"handle_container_exited_api_v1_internal_containers_exited_post","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/api/v1/internal/executions/{execution_id}/heartbeat":{"post":{"tags":["internal"],"summary":"Handle Execution Heartbeat","description":"处理执行心跳\n\n由 Executor 在执行过程中定期调用，保持执行活跃状态。","operationId":"handle_execution_heartbeat_api_v1_internal_executions__execution_id__heartbeat_post","parameters":[{"name":"execution_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Execution Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/v1/internal/executions/{execution_id}/result":{"post":{"tags":["internal"],"summary":"Report Execution Result","description":"上报执行结果\n\n由 Executor 在执行完成后调用，上报执行结果到控制平面。\n\n## 状态映射\n- API: `\"success\"` → Domain: `ExecutionStatus.COMPLETED`\n- API: `\"failed\"` → Domain: `ExecutionStatus.FAILED`\n- API: `\"timeout\"` → Domain: `ExecutionStatus.TIMEOUT`\n- API: `\"crashed\"` → Domain: `ExecutionStatus.CRASHED`\n\n## 幂等性\n- 如果执行记录已经是终态，返回 200（重复上报）\n- 如果是首次上报，更新后返回 201","operationId":"report_execution_result_api_v1_internal_executions__e